This comparison of unpatched publicly known vulnerabilities in latest stable version clients is based on vulnerabilities reports by [http://www.securityfocus.com/ SecurityFocus] and [https://secunia.com/ Secunia]. See [[Computer security#unpatched|computer security]] for more details about the importance of unpatched known flaws.
