The ethnographic and tourist complex called '''Cossack Village''' and St. Nicolas Crush of 18 century ({{lang-uk|Туристично-етнографічний комплекс "Козацький хутір" та церква Св. Миколая XVIII ст.}}) is an open-air museum, created for the National Historical and Cultural Preserve "Chyhyryn", located in the village of [[Stetsivka]].

[[File:Драбівці03.jpg|thumb|right| St. Nicolas Crush]]

