{{italic title}} [[File:Geometric mouse.JPG| thumb| ''Geometric Mouse, Variation I, Scale A'' ]] '''''Geometric Mouse, Variation I, Scale A''''' is an abstract sculpture by [[Claes Oldenburg]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://siris-artinventories.si.edu/ipac20/ipac.jsp?&profile=all&source=~!siartinventories&uri=full=3100001~!6328~!0#focus |title=Geometric Mouse, Variation I, Scale A, (sculpture) |website=Siris-artinventories.si.edu |date= |accessdate=2017-04-17}}</ref>
Examples are located at the [[Hirshhorn Museum and Sculpture Garden]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.waymarking.com/waymarks/WM4A6R |title="Geometric Mouse: Variation I, Scale A": by Claes Oldenburg - Hirshhorn Museum and Sculpture Garden, Washington D.C. - Abstract Public Sculptures on |website=Waymarking.com |date= |accessdate=2017-04-17}}</ref> [[Museum of Modern Art]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.moma.org/collection/object.php?object_id=81145 |title=Claes Oldenburg. Geometric Mouse, Scale A. 1975 |publisher=MoMA |date= |accessdate=2017-04-17}}</ref> and [[Walker Art Center]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://collections.walkerart.org/item/enlarge_fs.html?type=object&id=878&image_num=1 |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-04-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110929183645/http://collections.walkerart.org/item/enlarge_fs.html?type=object&id=878&image_num=1 |archivedate=2011-09-29 |df= }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://artsconnected.org/resource/91666/geometric-mouse-scale-a |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-04-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719083036/http://artsconnected.org/resource/91666/geometric-mouse-scale-a |archivedate=2011-07-19 |df= }}</ref>
